<plot>This Chuck Jones animated short parodies the newsreels that were the standard fare for movie theater intermissions during The Second World War. Included are gags about the food and supply shortages civilians had to suffer through, as well as the increasing role women were playing in the American war effort.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?600309</url></doc>
